		"description": "Full API collection for Mono Wear backend - Spring Boot 3.4.6\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Import collection + environment\n2. Run \"Register\" or \"Login\" → token auto-saved\n3. All authenticated requests use {{token}} automatically\n\n## Auth Flow\n- Register/Login → JWT token\n- Forgot Password → OTP → Verify OTP → Reset Password",
